On Sunday, October 02, 2005, at 03:24PM, john kolak <jkolak(-at-)gmail.com> wrote:

>Does anyone know what year seat belts were available as optional
>equipment and what year they became mandatory in California?

1966 was probably when manufacturers had to install them. Optional availability earlier would depend on the make and model I suppose.

The law requiring you to wear them in CA passed in 1986.

http://www.preventioninstitute.org/traffic_seatbelt.html

